Infographic: Why crime will be the biggest challenge for the BJP govt in UP 
14-3-2017 
Why crime will be the biggest challenge for the BJP govt in UP

UP is notorious for its shockingly bad crime statistics. It reportedly has the highest number of violent crimes in the country, accounting for almost 13% of all such incidents and the dubious distinction of the maximum incidence of crimes against women. All this compounded by the fact that the state also has among the lowest number of policemen per lakh of population. 
